                {
                  "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
                  "Text": "*\tBased on Mills et al (1997).\n\n*\tLysimeter (1.2 m deep by 1 m wide) trial conducted during the 1994/95 season.\n\n*\tLocation: Massey University, Palmerston North (40°2'S, 175°4'E.\n\n*\tSoil: Manawatu fine sandy loam.\n\n*\tPlant material: 4-year-old 'Braeburn' on MM106 rootstock \n\n*\tDate of full bloom (DAF): 20/10/1994\n\n*\tThree irrigation regimes: Control, Early Deficit, Late Deficit\n  ",
                  "Name": "Experiment description",
                  "ResourceName": null,
                  "Children": [],
                  "Enabled": false,
                  "ReadOnly": false
